snippet.title: Little Cells - Teaser
snippet.description:
"Little Cells" is a quick & simple puzzle action game, released on Windows, MacOs & Linux.
Google play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fullybugged.littlecells
Steam page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/352210
Other shops: http://littlecells.fullybugged.com:

Follow us on:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Fully.Bugged
Twitter: http://twitter.com/fullybugged
Mastodon: https://mastodon.gamedev.place/@FullyBugged
Discord: https://discord.gg/ZCMm2xw
